<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Cutpurse" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Cutpurse,</orth> a thief: <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.686" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 686</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.65" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 6, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.1.91" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.2.88" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 2, 88</bibl>. <cit><quote>a c. of the empire and the rule,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 99</bibl></cit>. Adjectively: <cit><quote>you c. rascal,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.137" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 137</bibl></cit>.
